* Unity Catalog\nNaming Requirements
** Object names
***_ Max 255 characters
***_ Stored in lowercase
***_ Case-insensitive matching
** Prohibited characters
***_ Periods (.)
***_ Spaces
***_ Forward slashes (/)
***_ ASCII control characters
** Allowed
***_ Hyphens (with backticks)
***_ Special chars via backticks
** Column names
***_ Casing preserved
***_ Case-insensitive queries
***_ Backticks for special chars
@endmindmap
